conbody.p:
 In the VisitorAPI / AppMeasurement Audience Manager Module
		  integrations, there will be two destination publishing iFrame requests made in
		  IE6-9: 
		  //fast.<subdomain>.demdex.net/dest5.html and

		  //fast.<subdomain>.demdex.net/dest4.html.
		  The correct behavior, as seen in other browsers, is to only load 
		  //fast.<subdomain>.demdex.net/dest5.html.
